Name: dbid
Description: The OID of the database the dependent object is in, or zero for a shared object or a SHARED_DEPENDENCY_PIN entry

Name: classid
Description: The OID of the system catalog the dependent object is in, or zero for a SHARED_DEPENDENCY_PIN entry

Name: objid
Description: The OID of the specific dependent object, or zero for a SHARED_DEPENDENCY_PIN entry

Name: objsubid
Description: For a table column, this is the column number (the objid and classid refer to the table itself). For all other object types, this column is zero.

Name: refclassid
Description: The OID of the system catalog the referenced object is in (must be a shared catalog)

Name: refobjid
Description: The OID of the specific referenced object

Name: deptype
Description: A code defining the specific semantics of this dependency relationship; see text
